properties = self.load_properties('testfile_uncertainty.yaml')
d = DataPoint(properties[0])
assert np.isclose(d.composition['H2'].amount.value, Q_(0.444))
assert np.isclose(d.composition['H2'].amount.error, Q_(0.00444))
